cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image reconstruction using autoencoder-based optimization techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of optimization techniques also falls under information theory (cs.IT) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the application of the proposed method to terahertz imaging falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
